OL,3,CWoman left with PTSD after being
OL,4,Cconned by romance fraudster
OL,6,FFiona met Millin in July 2021 at a
OL,7,Fwork event where she was told a series
OL,8,Fof heartbreaking stories about his
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News she fell in love
OL,12,Fwith a man who appeared kind-hearted
OL,13,Fand willing to do anything for anyone.
OL,15,FFiona said: "I felt really lucky to
OL,16,Fhave met someone so different. And it
OL,17,Fjust changed in an instant. It's crazy
OL,18,Fto think that I believed that version
OL,19,Fof him."
