OL,4,Cconned by romance fraudster
OL,6,FBen, who was a prolific gambler, had
OL,7,Fin fact targeted Fiona and invented a
OL,8,Fseries of lies to make her feel sorry
OL,9,Ffor him.
OL,11,FHe falsely claimed he was adopted, he
OL,12,Fhad an inherited heart condition, he
OL,13,Fhad a younger sister who died of
OL,14,Fcancer and his mum had been recently
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer.
OL,17,FThe deception can be seen played out
OL,18,Fover hundreds WhatsApp messages
OL,19,Fbetween the pair where Millin also
OL,20,Fclaimed he was a victim of fraud.
