OL,6,FHe said his bank accounts were frozen
OL,7,Fand his money was tied up in a house
OL,8,Fhe was selling with an unfaithful ex-
OL,9,Fpartner who had supposedly fallen
OL,10,Fpregnant to someone else.
OL,12,FMillin started asking Fiona for money
OL,13,Fto pay for bills, travel expenses and
OL,14,Fmore, which he promised he would pay
OL,15,Fback.
OL,17,FFiona said: "He'd send me a photo
OL,18,Fsaying the bank was closed and things
OL,19,Flike that. There was always an excuse
OL,20,For if he was at work he was too busy
OL,21,Fto go.
