OL,6,FDetective Claire Morgan from Avon and
OL,7,FSomerset Police started a larger
OL,8,Finvestigation looking into Millin in
OL,9,F2024, with four more women including
OL,10,FFiona.
OL,12,FShe said: "I would describe Millin as
OL,13,Fa very manipulative character. He has
OL,14,Fcreated these characters he introduces
OL,15,Fto females that were fraught with a
OL,16,Fweb of lives. Nothing he says to these
OL,17,Ffemales is the truth. And he relies on
OL,18,Fthose lies to be able to manipulate
OL,19,Fthose to give him money."
