OL,3,CWoman left with PTSD after being
OL,4,Cconned by romance fraudster
OL,6,F"In 18 years, I think Millin is the
OL,7,Fmost prolific I have come across. The
OL,8,Fweb of deceit is extremely large and
OL,9,Fthe way that he could maintain these
OL,10,Flies was beyond anything that I had
OL,11,Fseen before.
OL,13,F'He was using multiple mobile phone
OL,14,Fdevices and email addresses. He was
OL,15,Fvery aware of what he was doing."
OL,17,FAfter a long, painstaking
OL,18,Finvestigation, and thanks to the
OL,19,Ftestimony of the four women, Millin
OL,20,Fwas arrested and charged in the summer
OL,21,Fof 2025.
