OL,7,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,8,Frepresentation and was jailed for 36
OL,9,Fmonths. But Claire believes there may
OL,10,Fbe more victims.
OL,12,FShe said: "I don't think we've got all
OL,13,Fof Ben Millin's victims potentially. I
OL,14,Fthink there could be more out there we
OL,15,Fhaven't been able to identify. And
OL,16,Fthere will be others. This is a crime
OL,17,Fthat is underreported by victims. I
OL,18,Fthink they feel very embarrassed by
OL,19,Fthings that have happened, which they
OL,20,Fshouldn't at all."
